Title: I Am the Future
Writer: Grant Morrison (developed by), Brian Taylor (developed by), Matthew White, Matthew White (executive story editor), Ken Kristensen (story editor)
Actors: Christopher Meloni, Ritchie Coster, Lili Mirojnick, Medina Senghore
Plot: Sax and Happy are finally reunited and make a renewed push to find Hailey. Amanda gets in to trouble as she pursues a dangerous lead alone. Blue and Isabella feud over a dark family secret.
